 to evaluate impacts and resources conservation potential of composting: A case study of the Asti District in Italy (2008) Resour Conserv Recycl, 52 (12), pp. 1373-1381; Cadena, E., Colón, J., Sánchez, A., Font, A., Artola, A., A methodology to determine gaseous emissions in a composting plant (2009) Waste Manage, 29, pp. 2799-2807; (2001) California Compost Quality Council, , CCQC-compost maturity index, technical report. California; Chanakya, H.N., Ramachandra, T.V., Guruprasad, M., Devi, V., Micro-treatment options for components of organic fraction of MSW in residential areas (2007) Environ Monit Assess, 135, pp. 129-139; Colón, J., Martínez-Blanco, J., Gabarrell, X., Rieradevall, J., Font, X., Artola, A., Performance of an industrial biofilter from a composting plant in the removal of ammonia and VOCs after material replacement (2009) J Chem Technol Biotechnol, 84, pp. 1111-1117; Compostadores SL., , http://www.compostadores.com;2008, Home page; (1999) Council of the European Union., , Directive 1999/31/EC, of 26 April 1999 on the landfill of waste; Dalemo, M., Sonesson, U., Bjorklund, A., Mingarini, K., Frostell, B., Jonsson, H., ORWARE - A simulation model for organic waste handling systems 1: Model description (1997) Resour Conserv Recycl, 21, pp. 17-37; Diaz, R., Warith, M., Life-cycle assessment of municipal solid wastes: Development of the WASTED model (2006) Waste Manage, 26, pp. 886-901; Diggelman, C., Ham, R.K., Household food waste to wastewater or to solid waste? That is the question (2003) Waste Manage Res, 21, pp. 501-514; Ekvall, T., Tillman, A., Open-loop recycling: Criteria for allocation procedures (1997) Int J Life Cycle Assess, 2, pp. 155-162; (2008) Green Paper on the Management of Bio-waste in the European Union, , European Commission; (2005) Waste Generated and Treated in Europe, Luxembourg, , European Communities; Favoino, E., Hogg, D., The potential role of compost in reducing greenhouse gases (2008) Waste Manage Res, 26, pp. 61-69; Finn